PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771878798
OL,3,CFitness instructor takes on Great
OL,4,CWorld Race challenge for cancer charity
OL,6,FShe will fly first to Cape Town in
OL,7,FSouth Africa, before flying onto
OL,8,FAntartica for the first marathon. She
OL,9,Fwill return to Cape Town for the
OL,10,Fsecond, before flying on to Perth in
OL,11,FAustralia for the third.
OL,13,FFrom there, she will go on to Abu
OL,14,FDhabi, then to Portugal, followed by
OL,15,FCartagena in Colombia and then on to
OL,16,FMiami for the seventh and final
OL,17,Fmarathon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
