PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771878798
OL,3,CFitness instructor takes on Great
OL,4,CWorld Race challenge for cancer charity
OL,6,F"It's bonkers, completely bonkers."
OL,7,Fshe says: " When I signed up I thought
OL,8,Fit's just one run a day. But it's not
OL,9,Freally because some of them are only
OL,10,F11 hours apart, so I'll finish a
OL,11,Fmarathon, go straight to the airport,
OL,12,Fget on a plane, land in the next place
OL,13,Fand start running.
OL,15,F"There are no hotels, we will just
OL,16,Fsleep on the plane. I think the
OL,17,Frecovery stages will be hard because
OL,18,FI'm not good at sleeping on planes!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
