PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771878798
OL,3,CFitness instructor takes on Great
OL,4,CWorld Race challenge for cancer charity
OL,6,FVictoria registered for the challenge,
OL,7,Fdespite having only run distances of
OL,8,Ffive kilometres. She teaches Pilates,
OL,9,FYoga and Spin but says running is a
OL,10,Fnew challenge that's out of her
OL,11,Fcomfort zone. A gruelling training
OL,12,Fschedule is underway, supervised by an
OL,13,Fexpert coach from the challenge team.
OL,15,F"It's mad - I am questioning my life
OL,16,Fchoices daily at the moment!" she
OL,17,Flaughs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
