OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771878798
OL,3,CFitness instructor takes on Great
OL,4,CWorld Race challenge for cancer charity
OL,6,FBut behind Victoria's decision to take
OL,7,Fpart lies a desire to raise money for
OL,8,Fa charity close to her heart. She is
OL,9,Faiming to raise 150 thousand pounds
OL,10,Ffor Clatterbridge Cancer Charity.
OL,12,FHer husband Neil was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fthe disease last year and has been
OL,14,Freceiving Immunotherapy treatment from
OL,15,Fspecialist doctors there. He himself
OL,16,Fhas raised thousands for the charity
OL,17,Fafter losing his first wife to the
OL,18,Fdisease 15 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771878798
OL,3,CFitness instructor takes on Great
OL,4,CWorld Race challenge for cancer charity
OL,6,FVictoria said: "The charity is
OL,7,Fabsolutely phenomenal. The money that
OL,8,Fthey have ploughed into research and
OL,9,Fall of the help that they have given
OL,10,Fus is amazing, so I just thought, you
OL,11,Fknow what, I'm doing it."
OL,13,FNeil said; "I know she will put the
OL,14,Fwork in, she is out all hours every
OL,15,Fday doing long, long runs. I am so
OL,16,Fproud of her and so grateful that
OL,17,Fshe's doing it for Clatterbridge. And
OL,18,FI'm very grateful that she's doing it
OL,19,Ffor me."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
